import React from "react"
import {
  BrowserRouter as Router,
  Routes,
  Route,
  NavLink,
} from "react-router-dom"
import {
  MDBBreadcrumb,
  MDBBreadcrumbItem,
  MDBContainer,
} from "mdb-react-ui-kit"

export default function App() {
  return (
    <MDBContainer className="py-2">
      <MDBBreadcrumb>
        <NavLink className="breadcrumb-item" to="/" activeclassname="active">
          Home
        </NavLink>
        <NavLink
          className="breadcrumb-item"
          to="/games"
          activeclassname="active"
        >
          Games
        </NavLink>
        <NavLink
          className="breadcrumb-item"
          to="/wheel-of-fortune"
          activeclassname="active"
        >
          Wheel of Fortune
        </NavLink>
      </MDBBreadcrumb>
    </MDBContainer>
  )
}
